dev.jeka.core.api.depmanagement

Class JkModuleDependency.JkArtifactSpecification

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.jeka.core.api.depmanagement.JkModuleDependency.JkArtifactSpecification
  • Enclosing class:
    JkModuleDependency

    public static class JkModuleDependency.JkArtifactSpecification
extends java.lang.Object
    When declaring a module dependency, we implicitly request for the main artifact of this module. Nevertheless, we can request for getting others artifacts in place or additionally of the main one. This class aims at specifying which artifact are we interested for the dependency.
